: "# geox_load_seismic_line

> **Type:** Tool  
> **Risk Level:** GUARDED  
> **Epistemic Level:** OBS (raw data loading)  
> **Confidence:** 0.99  
> **Certainty Band:** [0.98, 1.00]  
> **Tags:** [tool, seismic, data_loading, f4, f11]  
> **arifos_floor:** F4, F11  

---

## Purpose

Load 2D or 3D seismic data with full provenance tracking and F4 Clarity validation. This is the **entry point** for all seismic interpretation workflows.

**Critical Principle:** Raw seismic data is OBS (observational). All downstream interpretation is DER/INT/SPEC and must be explicitly labeled.

---

## Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-----------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| `filepath` | string | Yes | — | Absolute or relative path to SEG-Y, ZGY, or HDF5 |
| `crs` | string | Yes | — | Coordinate reference system (EPSG code or WKT) |
| `survey_id` | string | Yes | — | Unique survey identifier for provenance |
| `inline_range` | [int, int] | No | [null, null] | Subset: [start_inline, end_inline] |
| `xline_range` | [int, int] | No | [null, null] | Subset: [start_xline, end_xline] |
| `time_range_ms` | [float, float] | No | [null, null] | Time window: [t_min_ms, t_max_ms] |
| `sample_decimation` | int | No | 1 | Spatial decimation factor (1=no decimation) |
| `lazy_load` | bool | No | true | Load metadata only, data on demand |

---

## F4 Clarity Validation

The tool **rejects** loading if any of these are missing or invalid:

| Check | Violation | Consequence |
|-------|-----------|-------------|
| CRS parseable | Invalid EPSG or malformed WKT | **REJECT** — cannot locate on Earth |
| Spatial bounds valid | Requested subset outside survey extent | **REJECT** — data does not exist |
| Sample interval consistent | Header value ≠ actual data spacing | **WARNING** — may indicate corruption |
| Trace header integrity | Missing or malformed headers | **WARNING** — partial data loss possible |

---

## F11 Authority (Provenance)

Required metadata extracted from file headers:

```yaml
provenance:
  survey_id: "MB_2024_3D"
  acquisition_date: "2023-08-15"
  contractor: "PGS"
  vessel: "Ramform Sterling"
  sample_interval_ms: 4.0
  record_length_ms: 6000.0
  inline_range: [100, 2500]
  xline_range: [1000, 3500]
  crs: "EPSG:32648"
  file_format: "ZGY v2.0"
  file_hash: "sha256:abc123..."
```

