## Error Handling

| Error | Cause | Resolution |
|-------|-------|------------|
| `F4_CRS_INVALID` | Malformed EPSG code | Verify CRS with epsg.io |
| `F4_BOUNDS_OUT_OF_RANGE` | Subset outside survey | Check inline/xline ranges |
| `F11_FILE_CORRUPT` | Checksum mismatch | Verify file transfer integrity |
| `F11_METADATA_INCOMPLETE` | Missing required headers | Contact data provider |

